summary: J\'zargo new better look. Just enjoy.
descriptionHtml:
[center][img]http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/images/10231-1-1329565462.png[/img]

[b]Hello again.[/b]
Another mod from my better looking series. Now its time for J\'zargo in his Puss in Boots version. I have consider of making him Zevran Aranei, but there is a problem... He speking of khajit to much. So! There he is! You Puss in boots J\'Zargo! No more mustach! No more sad colour. Now he have big orange eyes (I know Poos have green, but i prefere orange). Lovly orange fur... And what to say more? Just enjoy!

And I forget to inform you that he dont have hood. Becose i wanna give you possibility to make him wear whatever you desire.

And... Now you can marry him as well : ) Destruction mage husband for everyone!
[img]http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/images/10231-1-1329565637.png[/img]
